 Will get overwritten by `SpawnPotentials`

Delay.description: The number of ticks until the next spawn

SpawnCount.description: The number of entities that will be placed

RequiredPlayerRange.description: The radius in blocks that a player has to be within to spawn entities

MinSpawnDelay.description: The minimum random delay for the next spawn

MaxSpawnDelay.description: The maximum random delay for the next spawn

Fuel.description: The number of ticks until the fuel runs out

TNTFuse.description: The number of ticks until this TNT minecart explodes

LastOutput.description: The last output of this command block minecart

TrackOutput.description: Whether the command block minecart should track its output

Command.description: The command stored in this command block minecart

SuccessCount.description: The success count of the last command

Item.description: The item in the item frame

Invisible.description:
Whether the item frame should be invisible
 The item inside the frame is not effected

Fixed.description: Whether the item frame should not be able to be broken and should disallow the item to be moved

TileX.description: The x coordinate of the block the item frame is in

ItemDropChance.description: The chance the item has to drop

TileY.description: The y coordinate of the block the item frame is in

Facing.description: The direction the item frame is facing

TileZ.description: The z coordinate of the block the item frame is in

Fuse.description: The number of ticks until this tnt explodes

Warmup.description: The number of ticks until the fangs pop out of the ground

yTile.description: The y coordinate of the projectile

xTile.description: The x coordinate of the projectile

LeftOwner.description: Whether the projectile has left its owner

Owner.description: The UUID of the projectile's owner

zTile.description: The z coordinate of the projectile

inBlockState.description: The block the projectile is in

Item.description: The item representation of the projectile

pickup.description: How players can pick up the projectile

crit.description: Whether the projectile should do critical damage

ShotFromCrossbow.description: Whether the projectile was shot from a crossbow

PierceLevel.description: The number of entities to pass through

SoundEvent.description: The sound event to play when the projectile hits something

life.description: The number of ticks since the projectile last moved

inGround.description: Whether the projectile is in the ground

player.description: Whether a player shot the projectile

damage.description: The damage the projectile should do

Color.description:
The color of the arrow  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

CustomPotionColor.description:
The color of the arrow's particles  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

CustomPotionEffects.description: The custom potion effects to give to the hit entity

Potion.description: The name of the default potion effect

Duration.description: The number of ticks the glowing effect lasts

DealtDamage.description: Whether the trident has damaged an entity already

ShowBottom.description: Whether to show the base of the end crystal

BeamTarget.description: The block that the beam is pointing to

Y.description: The y coordinate of the block the beam is pointing to

Z.description: The z coordinate of the block the beam is pointing to

X.description: The x coordinate of the block the beam is pointing to

WaitTime.description: The number of ticks until the area effect cloud appears

DurationOnUse.description: The amount the duration changes when the area effect cloud is used

ReapplicationDelay.description: The number of ticks until the effects are reapplied

Age.description:
The number of ticks this area effect cloud has been alive  
 The area effect cloud will disappear when greater than `Duration + WaitTime`

RadiusOnUse.description: The change in the radius of the area effect cloud when it is used

Radius.description: The radius of the area effect cloud

RadiusPerTick.description: The change in the radius of the area effect cloud per tick

Color.description:
The color of the particles  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

Particle.description: The particle the area effect cloud displays

Duration.description: The maximum number of ticks until this area effect cloud will disappear after `WaitTime` is done

Effects.description: The potion effects that get applied on use

LeftOfUpsideDownDiagonal.description: Left of upside-down Diagonal (Per bend inverted)

RightOfDiagonal.description: Right of Diagonal (Per bend sinister inverted)

Percentage.description:
For every modifier, multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the amount of the particular modifier.
 Functions the same as Operation 1 if there is only a single modifier with operation 1 or 2.
 However, for multiple modifiers it will multiply the modifiers rather than adding them

Multiplicative.description:
Multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the sum of the modifiers' amounts.

Additive.description: Adds all of the modifiers' amounts to the current value of the attribute
